    "podcast_intro": "Welcome to this week's fertility and reproductive medicine news roundup. I'm your host, and today we're covering the latest research and clinical developments from across the field — from trying to conceive naturally and preconception care, to IVF, endometriosis, male factor infertility, and beyond.",
